00:10:02.600 --> 00:10:09.800
209, 174, 63 wait.

00:10:09.800 --> 00:10:15.348
All right, that
seems reasonable.

00:10:15.348 --> 00:10:16.640
Let's see if other folks agree.

00:10:16.640 --> 00:10:19.610
And again, just like
last time, these things

00:10:19.610 --> 00:10:21.350
