to interpretation.

00:10:21.350 --> 00:10:24.470
Hopefully, actually, this
mix is pretty prescribed,

00:10:24.470 --> 00:10:26.490
but this is up to your judgment.

00:10:26.490 --> 00:10:28.970
So we're expecting some
different answers here.

00:10:31.860 --> 00:10:34.760
So this time we've got,
basically because we

00:10:34.760 --> 00:10:37.550
constrained the problem down,
these answers tend to agree,

00:10:37.550 --> 00:10:41.630
these are still, people
have different opinions

00:10:41.630 --> 00:10:42.930
about different things.

00:10:42.930 --> 00:10:44.970
And so we have a
fair range there.

00:10:44.970 --> 00:10:47.750
But it does look
like, as an over all,

00:10:47.750 --> 00:10:49.790
that this isn't a bad process.

00:10:49.790 --> 00:10:51.980
There's more value added
than non value added.

00:10:51.980 --> 00:10:54.688
So that's pretty good, actually.

